PrecisApproval to enter into an ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT PARTNERSHIP AGREEMENT with each of the Provinces of Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba and Saskatchewan which will provide a mechanism for achieving greater federal- provincial cooperation in realizing the economic and regional development potential of the provinces by way of complementary and focused approaches.

precis:
Approval to enter into an ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT PARTNERSHIP AGREEMENT with
each of the Provinces of Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba and
Saskatchewan which will provide a mechanism for achieving greater federal-
provincial cooperation in realizing the economic and regional development
potential of the provinces by way of complementary and focused approaches.
